sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User as 👤 User / Browser
  participant Server as ⚙️ Fastify Server
  participant CF as 🛡️ Cloudflare Turnstile
  participant DB as 🗄️ SQLite Database

  Note over User, DB: Step 1: User Login Flow (POST /api/v1/auth/login)
  User->>CF: Get CAPTCHA turnstileToken
  CF-->>User: Return turnstileToken
  User->>Server: POST /api/v1/auth/login <br>[username, password, turnstileToken, x-hw-signature, _em_device]
  
  opt Turnstile Configured
      Server->>CF: Verify turnstileToken (siteverify)
      CF-->>Server: Return success: true
  end
  
  Server->>DB: Query User by username
  DB-->>Server: Return User info & passwordHash
  Server->>Server: Verify password (argon2.verify)
  
  alt Device Binding Check
      Server->>DB: Query registered_devices for userId & deviceToken
      DB-->>Server: Return binding record
      alt Device is not registered
          Server-->>User: Response 460 Access Denied (device_not_registered)
      else Device registered & matches hardware signature
          Note over Server: Device authorized
      end
  end

  Server->>DB: Create Session & store refreshToken hash
  DB-->>Server: Confirm session stored
  Server-->>User: Response 200 OK [accessToken, user details] <br>(Set-Cookie: refreshToken, _em_device)

  Note over User, DB: Step 2: Token Refresh Flow (POST /api/v1/auth/refresh)
  User->>Server: POST /api/v1/auth/refresh (with refreshToken cookie + fingerprint)
  Server->>DB: Verify session (find refreshToken, check not revoked/expired)
  DB-->>Server: Return Session details
  Server->>DB: Rotate Refresh Token: Revoke old, insert new Session
  DB-->>Server: Confirm rotation stored
  Server-->>User: Response 200 OK [accessToken] <br>(Set-Cookie: new refreshToken)
